<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-us">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/login.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Righteous&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Bubbble Login Portal</title>


</head>
<body class="<%= weather %>">
    <header>
        <img src="/images/<%= weather %>.png" alt="<%= weather %> Icon">
        <h1>Welcome to Bubbble</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
    <div class="left-column">
        <h2>What is Bubbble?</h2>
        <p>Well we are a social media site where everything is weather themed. When you create a post, it is themed
            according to the weather at your location. There are some neat color schemes and CSS that go into the designs! 
            There are a number of different weather designs you will see:
        </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Clear Sky</li>
                <li>Cloudy</li>
                <li>Rain</li>
                <li>Mist</li>
                <li>Snow</li>
                <li>Thunderstorm</li>
            </ul>
    </div> <!--left column-->

    <div class="right-column">
        <%= message %>
        <div class="form-card">
            <h3>Sign into Bubbble</h3>
            <form action="/signIn" method="post">
                <label>Username</label><br>
                <input required type="text" name="username"><br>
                <label>Password</label><br>
                <input required type="password" name="password"><br>
                <input type="submit" value="Sign In">
                <p class="message"></p>
            </form>


            <h3>Or sign up!</h3>
            <form action="/register" method="post">
                <label>First Name*</label><br>
                <input required type="text" name="fname"><br>
                <label>Last Name*</label><br>
                <input required type="text" name="lname"><br>

                <label>Username*</label><br>
                <input required type="text" name="username"><br>
                <label>Password*</label><br>
                <input required type="password" name="password"><br>
                
                <label>Reenter Password*</label><br>
                <input required type="password" name="password2"><br>    
                
                <input type="submit" value="Register">

            </form>
            
        </div> <!--form card-->

    </div> <!--right column-->
    </main>
</body>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; Ethan Tindall 2021 - CSE341: Backend 2 - Project 2</p>
</footer>
</html>
    